Random notes

Objects:
- Stage
- Each stage has a number of 'stage units' which represent a fraction of the stage
- Each stage has a number of candelabras
- Each candelabra has a number of candles

STAGE:
- Is square, broken up into a number of stage units
- Height and width in e.g. m, stage units are e.g. 1cm each
- The value in each square represents the amount of light on that spot given the current configuration
- There are two values for each square, one for the light at ground level and one at around 6 foot (or can be adjusted)

